# ==============================================================================
# Educational Note
# ==============================================================================
# This .gitignore protects personal data while keeping the project
# structure, methodology, and technical innovation visible.
# 
# The goal is to share:
# - Technical architecture and innovation
# - Cat-centric ethical framework 
# - Emergent AI behavior research methodology
# - Philosophical approach to AI safety
# - Conway's Game of Life + AI integration
# - Multi-agent system design patterns
#
# While protecting:
# - Personal information and photos
# - API keys and credentials  
# - Actual simulation data
# - Financial/health information
# - Production deployment details
#
# "Share the chaos, protect the cats" 🐱‍💻